<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-015.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 遇敵：<span style='text-decoration: underline;'>
<span style='color: #000080;'><a href='./ff2_images/ff2_enemy_list/125.png' target='_blank'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>125-提亞馬特</span></a></span></span> ( HP 5000／弱點：神經／吸收：冰火雷毒 )<br /> 攻略：盡量用無屬性攻擊方式，這傢伙只會放些全體魔法，傷害都不高</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-016.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 繼續回到 4F，這次走最左側的 A 路線</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-017.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 單線走到左側後，左前方會有暗道，過去後往上直走</p>
