<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-019.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 遇敵：<span style='text-decoration: underline;'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>
<a href='./ff2_images/ff2_enemy_list/047.png' target='_blank'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>047-僵屍伯根</span></a></span></span> ( HP 2500／<span style='color: #ff0000;'>弱點：火、治療</span>／吸收冰 )<br /> 攻略：這傢伙其實蠻廢的，裝備治癒之杖敲他會有意想不到的效果&#8230;XDDDD</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-020.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 從寶箱下面走幾步路很快的繞到上面，直接往右，<span style='color: #ff0000;'>連續穿過兩次牆上暗道</span></p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-021.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 到了最右上角有根柱子，在柱子右下方還有一個暗道，往右進去</p>
