<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-023.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 回到 4F，走最後一個 C 主線前進</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-024.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 到了 6F 單線走到中間處，往左側暗道穿過去</p>
