<span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'><a href='./ff2_images/ff2_enemy_list/127.png' target='_blank'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>127-阿斯塔羅特</span></a></span></span> )，接著再穿過左邊暗道往下</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-026.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 遇敵：<span style='text-decoration: underline;'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>
<a href='./ff2_images/ff2_enemy_list/127.png' target='_blank'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>127-阿斯塔羅特</span></a></span></span> ( HP 7000／弱點無 )<br /> 攻略：裝備剛到手的 <span style='color: #800000;'>正宗</span> 狂砍，再用 <span style='color: #800080;'>核爆、究極</span> 去轟吧！</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-027.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 前往最左下角的傳送點，會傳到 4F 的另一邊</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-028.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 最後一次來 4F 了，只有單線，走到盡頭繼續傳送就會前往 7F 了</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff2_images/ff2_part_7/01-pandemonium-029.png' width='486' height='326' /></p>
